<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Dinkelsbühl</head><p>Der Rat begrüßt die Zusammenkunft mehrerer Städte zu Ulm und das Schreiben an den König wegen der minderwertigen goldenen Münze, bittet um Nachricht bei Antwort und kündigt in selber Sache bald eine Gesandtschaft zum König an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_60" id="28v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l11">Der Stat cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l13">Dinkelſpühel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l15"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als vns <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſame freuntſchaft <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von <expan>ſölch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l17">
<del rend="strikethrough">der </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l16">groſſen </ab></add> <expan>geprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wegen / als in die guldein Müncʒe <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l18">geuallen ſind / vvie daʒ gemain Stete 
<del rend="strikethrough">dan </del> ſich darumb cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l19">vlm miteinander vnter redt vnd ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l20">dem <expan>Römiſche<ex>n</ex></expan> künig <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſölch prüche cʒu vnderſten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l21">vnd <expan>ʒufürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd geuellt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l22"> vns cʒemal wol / 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ ſie eʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_line_1574242046400_1276">
<del rend="strikethrough">das </del></ab></add> getan / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_line_1574242049544_1281">daʒ </ab></add> ſie die ſache <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l24">gar weiſlich vnd <expan>redlichn</expan> fürſich genomen <expan>habn</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_line_1576657408972_3849"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vns dunkt daʒ </ab><ab facs="#facs_60_line_1576657411860_3854">das <expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>leute<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_60_line_1576657416035_3859">ein groſʒ notdurft ſeẏ </ab></add> vnd wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l26"><expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſamen freuntſchaft <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_line_1574242115585_1296"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> </ab></add> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreibens</expan> mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l28"><expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / vnd <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr erſamkeit fleiſʒiklich / Seẏ eʒ / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l30">
<del rend="strikethrough">ew </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der künig <expan>gemaine<ex>n</ex></expan> Steten 
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l29">eın antvvurt </ab></add> darauff tun werde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l31">daʒ Jr vns <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> auch wiſſen laſſen wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l32"><expan>Alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weiſheit das <expan>füglich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeẏ / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l33">v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan></del> in <expan>ſölche<ex>n</ex></expan> oder <expan>mer<ex>ern</ex></expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l34"> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> / Auch 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſo </del> laſſen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>weiſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> wiſſen / daʒ wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_line_1574242295352_1320">willen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> erber botſchaft 
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_line_1576657419169_3864">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>kürcʒlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l36"> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem ~ künig cʒetun / vnd ſeinen 
<del rend="strikethrough">gnad </del> <expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> gnaden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l37">
<del rend="strikethrough">auch </del> <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>geprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch fürtragen vnd ercʒelen laſſen <gap reason="illegible"/></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l39">
<del rend="strikethrough">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat wegen </del> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>voc<ex>em</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l40"><expan>Jocund<ex>it</ex>at<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_60" id="28v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der Stat czu Dinkelspühel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als uns <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        ersame freuntschaft <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von
                                <expan>sölch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>grossen</add>
<expan>geprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wegen, als in die guldein müncze
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und gevallen sind, wie daz gemain
                        stete sich darumb czu Ulm miteinander unter redt und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> künig,
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, sölch prüche czu understen und
                                <expan>zufürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>; und gevellt uns czemal wol,
                            <add>daz</add> sie die sache <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> gar weislich
                        und <expan>redlichn</expan> fürsich genomen <expan>habn</expan>
<add><expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> uns dunkt, daz das
                                <expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>leute<ex>n</ex></expan>
                            ein grosz notdurft sey</add>; und wir <expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamen freuntschaft
                            <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan></add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibens</expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr ersamkeit fleisziklich, sey ez
                        daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der künig, <expan>gemaine<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        steten <add>ein antwurt</add> darauff tun werde, daz ir uns
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> auch wissen lassen wöllet,
                                <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit das <expan>füglich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sey, das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>sölche<ex>n</ex></expan> oder
                                <expan>mer<ex>ern</ex></expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. Auch lassen wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> wissen, daz wir willen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> erber
                        botschaft <add>von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> stat
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan>kürczlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem künig, czetun und seinen
                                <expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> gnaden
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch fürtragen und erczelen lassen <app>
<note><gap reason="illegible"/>.</note>
</app>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>voc<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>jocund<ex>it</ex>at<ex>is</ex></expan>. </ab></div>
